d a series of locative quasi-verbs and focus particles sensitive to pragmatic factors like certainty.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 17. Dez 2021) 0aDogon languagexGrammar. 0aDogon languagexPhonology. 7aLANGUAGE ARTS & DISCIPLINES / Linguistics / General.2bisacsh  aDogon.  aLinguistic Typology.  aMalian Languages.  aText Linguistics.  aTone Language.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA Backlist Complete English Language 2000-2014 PART1z978311023857008iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA Backlist Linguistics and Semiotics  2000-2014 (EN)z978311023845708iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA Linguistics and Semiotics 2000 - 2014z9783110636970oZDB-23-DLS08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDe Gruyter Mouton Backlist 2000-2015z978311074296108iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertE-BOOK GESAMTPAKET / COMPLETE PACKAGE 2013z9783110317350oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertE-BOOK PACKAGE ENGLISH LINGUISTICS 2013z978311031724408iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertE-BOOK PAKET LINGUISTIK 2013z9783110317237oZDB-23-DSP0 cprintz978311030092540uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978311030107640uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783110301076423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783110301076/original  a978-3-11-023845-7  DGBA Backlist Linguistics and Semiotics  2000-2014 (EN)c2000d2014  a978-3-11-023857-0  DGBA Backlist Complete English Language 2000-2014 PART1c2000d2014  a978-3-11-031724-4  E-BOOK PACKAGE ENGLISH LINGUISTICS 2013b2013  a978-3-11-074296-1  De Gruyter Mouton Backlist 2000-2015c2000d2015  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_LS  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBACKALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_ECL_LS  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_ESSHALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA13ENGE